CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 19, 1945, pg. 13, reads: "Poster Contest winners-- Winners in high school competition sponsored by the Pittsburgh Branch of Federal Union, Inc, pose with their entries at Carnegie Museum. Left to right: Joseph Schumacher, junior at Connelly Vocational School; John Wall, senior at Peabody High; Roland Lucas, senior at Peabody High; Roland Lucas, Senior at South Hills High. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Roland Lucas holding sign inscribed "Federal Union, Divide and Conquer, Unite and Win"
